sorcer.util.bdb.objects
Class SorcerDatabase

java.lang.Object
  sorcer.util.bdb.objects.SorcerDatabase

public class SorcerDatabase
extends Object

SorcerDatabase defines the storage containers, indices and foreign keys for the service provider database persisting common SORCER objects.

Author:
Mike Sobolewski
